strings.Value: "I know of the pain you've endured in your life, but that doesn't excuse the atrocities you committed!"
"These lands can only have one ruler. That's why you'll die here."
[Spit on the Stag Lord] "Ha! What a wimp! I have no idea why everyone was so scared about you."

"I can't... fall... After so long, I learned to stand, I..." {n}The Stag Lord clutches something resembling a charm in his bloody fingers, seemingly placing the last of his hope into it. You hear a snapping sound, and then a dull sigh bursts from the Stag Lord's chest.{/n}
"Spare me your... compassion, your judgment. I... I'll sleep now. I'll wait for her... my dream..."
"What do you know... about crimes? I couldn't... tolerate... I did everything she..."
"These lands... are cursed... We'll see if you... live here longer than I..."
"Sometimes I... wonder that myself... Was it my own doing... or her blessing..."
